 Investigate Compromised Docker Containers with Falco
Learning Objectives
By completing this lab, you will:

Install and configure Falco for real-time container security monitoring
Analyze container runtime events and detect suspicious activities
Investigate and respond to container security incidents using Falco rules
Generate and interpret security alerts from compromised containers
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of Linux command line
Familiarity with Docker containers
Knowledge of system security concepts
Understanding of log analysis fundamentals
